			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Gordon can you give us a &quot;PR&quot; reason why Ring of the Dead was taken out of the game? <BR>
I don't think this is a &quot;PR&quot; reason... but... <BR>
It was removed because it was out-of-character for a melee class to have the item. It was decided a long time ago that only the pure casters would have the ability to bind anywhere. <BR>
<BR>
&quot;We don't tell the users if a items drops any more or if we have decreased the amount it drops&quot; I asked why they did this with the Manastone and Rubicite Armor.<BR>
<BR>
We have on occasion made exceptions to what we've announced just to head off the complaints that come whenever we remove something. We didn't, for example, announce the removal of the Manastone until people noticed it on their own. <BR>
<BR>
-Gordon<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
Can you belive this??? I have been working on this damn quest for more than 6th month. Guess it is time to go get a life now. Thank you Verant!!<BR>
<BR>
Jorren Y`Kelt<BR>
42 Shadowkinght <BR>
Rathe Server<BR>

